🧭 Important reality check

Even after installing CUDA toolkit:

👉 You STILL do NOT need to reinstall:

NVIDIA driver
X11
GPU configuration

Your current system remains untouched.

🚨 If anything goes wrong (rollback plan)

If CUDA install breaks something:

sudo apt remove --purge cuda-toolkit-12-5
sudo apt autoremove

Driver will remain intact.

